rvenciones","guid":"oaGRaPD5t6RtaJ3N8XZeIQ","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Intentar control hemostático si hay sangrado activo","guid":"uxrQGrDa94mJwhgO7DYUHg","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"• Iniciar ★terapia\\Ncombinada:","guid":"XRl3KKupsYDHH_ZyCfIV-w","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"› **Corticosteroides** (ej., **metilprednisolona**)","guid":"diIHqJzvtpX0e4YLmCD0Yw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"› MÁS **Inmunoglobulina Intravenosa** (**IVIG**)","guid":"sVJl3FT_G0NFE366YhyFBQ","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"› MÁS Transfusiones de plaquetas según necesidad","guid":"ywEUgwpv_gZErxF3miPs5g","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"151","text":"• Si no hay respuesta: Considerar agonista del receptor de trombopoyetina\\N(**TPO-RA**) (ej., **romiplostim**)","guid":"UbP9n4K_xlmjfP7yTTDakw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"142","text":"› Manejo No Urgente\\N(Según presentación)","guid":"ZL2yGOWsKXQYjRG2UfSa5g","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"◊ Pacientes sin síntomas o con\\Nsangrado mucocutáneo menor","guid":"eT23KuYsv-efiSf0qJukBA","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• ★ Manejo Conservador\\N(Observación) preferido para:","guid":"jBVwdIjiG8ftH0hT8FKfww","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"› Adultos con recuento plaquetario ≥ 30,000/mm³","guid":"S0CBlx1yFDC3WE1n8PvbYg","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"› Niños con cualquier recuento plaquetario","guid":"iE5KuekfwpbtS1Pw1hKxMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"• Todos: Seguimiento regular por hematología\\Ny consejería sobre riesgos de sangrado.","guid":"MWKaNNv0Q0mpXVW1BjRQ3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"158","text":"◊ Pacientes con sangrado mucocutáneo significativo no vital o síntomas que\\Nimpactan calidad de vida / Adultos asintomáticos con plaquetas < 30,000/mm³","guid":"raAoPdQr1T9by4zKxLMCHA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"0","text":"• ★ Terapia Médica\\Nde Primera Línea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"› Indicada para adultos (plaquetas < 30,000/mm³)","guid":"oLRumAFUUcUTlUmwZqPmVQ","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"› Puede considerarse en niños (si sangrado significativo/QoL afectada)","guid":"gjsJF4kNoutyQp23jIhwYg","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"› Opciones preferidas:\\N**Corticosteroides**","guid":"SMemZzIj4hcUoPGC0K9RWg","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"• **Dexametasona**","guid":"KrCRjq7J1g3Ofzv8YP7Hrg","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"• O **Prednisona**","guid":"g3Os3yaPDP7EuYwXpibE5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"165","text":"› Alternativas (si contraindicación/no\\Nrespuesta/intolerancia a corticoides):","guid":"otTbFTvLkaz88V-H2v03GA","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• **Inmunoglobulina Intravenosa** (**IVIG**)","guid":"mjajL-mgO8aaxlPKxX4n8Q","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"◊ Efectos secundarios: ej., trombosis, meningitis aséptica, reacciones a la infusión","guid":"PfLxeKUQXTL4tBwYw1GU0g","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"◊ Urinalisis (pre-terapia, 2h y 4h post)","guid":"QgEivMniDJZj72Fa0-L6lA","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"• O **Inmunoglobulina Anti-Rho(D)**","guid":"bR4DRLAr-gO3jilLueD9Uw","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"◊ ★ Advertencia **FDA**: Riesgo de hemólisis intravascular","guid":"pLqRcKXplpkLW0tPiM8G8w","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"◊ Monitorización hospitalaria recomendada (mínimo 8h post-administración)","guid":"R0Yit3Trf8Cx4dy1NenJxg","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"◊ Solicitar estudio de hemólisis si síntomas característicos (dolor espalda, escalofríos, cambio color orina)","guid":"QK5bg_L47THf8Fk5qe2oQw","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"175","text":"◊ Efectos secundarios: ★ Hemólisis intravascular (potencialmente fatal)\\N→ anemia, disfunción multiorgánica, LRA, fallo renal, CID, muerte","guid":"5BmUHjRWSPKyKOQ-Z_HsrA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"165","text":"› ★ Opciones Terapéuticas Subsecuentes (PTI\\Nrefractaria/persistente/crónica - consultar especialista)","guid":"fWoDr39_4jcLYin8vh31Gw","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"◊ Agonistas del Receptor de\\NTrombopoyetina (**TPO-RAs**)","guid":"YebbSQDW0MN-ukbhv2m-yg","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• **Romiplostim**","guid":"HheS5sElD6JILOrH6IQm0A","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"• **Eltrombopag**","guid":"H2qtiIOXyZ6IqIk0l1_DJg","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"• **Avatrombopag**","guid":"HVFR16zoEJ5k9_2NZ4n0IQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"◊ **Rituximab**","guid":"13rs17xR2-WmVIEPuVmheQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"180","text":"◊ **Esplenectomía**","guid":"-Vt5_YJDLz3Jku8Gs_pgNw","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"• Indicaciones: Trombocitopenia resistente a\\Ntratamiento > **12 meses**, sangrado severo sin\\Nrespuesta a otros tratamientos","guid":"W56dwtXA7gLDKSU1X_PchA","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"• Procedimiento: Cirugía laparoscópica\\Nmínimamente invasiva preferida","guid":"NBCm4cip5IvY8LjBxQ_rUg","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"• Complicaciones: Ver\\N“Sepsis Asplénica”","guid":"lPzSFFvAfFPIz-pexIG8PQ","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"186","text":"• Prevención de complicaciones: Ver\\N“Manejo de pacientes asplénicos”","guid":"J82N10osUL76UGGWSNhcEQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"165","text":"› Disposición (Decisión\\Nde hospitalización)","guid":"0A5iAN0F7ACnE8cPJVjwdw","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"◊ Considerar admisión\\Nhospitalaria para:","guid":"W3Yi2v82pYfgJ1-wUPImWg","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"• Pacientes que requieren\\Ntratamiento de emergencia","guid":"Kwgmy73hFTr1SF6daS_OcA","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"• Deterioro funcional significativo o\\Nriesgo de hemorragia importante","guid":"KrJBbLYQvfRZnVxqbZQo6A","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"• Adultos\\Nasintomáticos/mínimamente\\Nsintomáticos con plaquetas <\\N20,000/mm³","guid":"CdM9uBYISP7SJqHf4FgbSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"191","text":"◊ Manejo ambulatorio\\Napropiado para:","guid":"Mog7LSxieNBRPkmk2Z7lew","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Pacientes en\\Nmanejo conservador","guid":"qaoF3wJLxkB5LO0d46uyiA","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"• Adultos asintomáticos/mínimamente\\Nsintomáticos recibiendo terapia de primera línea\\Ncon plaquetas 20,000–29,999/mm³","guid":"qxXzc0t0MvhVAuyKOvII-g","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"• Niños (típicamente ambulatorio\\Nindependientemente del nivel plaquetario,\\Nsalvo deterioro funcional/emergencia)","guid":"5IBavU-IPjhefpaHGIeZ_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"191","text":"◊ Pacientes ambulatorios:\\NSeguimiento hematológico\\Nexpedito (en **24–72 horas**)","guid":"dPMd-RU-ewP_DFiP1i6fHQ","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":200,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"AMBOSS. PTI-2025-1","id":"map_1046","resolved_references":[]}